longBusinessSummary: Vodafone Qatar P.Q.S.C., together with its subsidiaries, provides cellular mobile telecommunication and fixed-line broadband services for consumers and businesses in Qatar. It offers voice, messaging, data, fixed communications, Internet of Things, and ICT managed services, as well as sells related equipment and accessories. The company also provides postpaid and prepaid plans, home internet, bill payment, recharge, roaming, transfer number and balance, cloud and hosting, critical communication, fleet management, asset tracking, and security services, as well as electronic payment services. Vodafone Qatar P.Q.S.C. was incorporated in 2008 and is headquartered in Doha, Qatar.
